I"ó<p>FedRAMP updated the <a href="https://www.fedramp.gov/assets/resources/templates/FedRAMP-POAM-Template.xlsm" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Plan of Actions and Milestones (POA&amp;M) template</a> to include two new columns. The additional columns were added at the behest of agency partners to help them track Cybersecurity and Infrastructure Security Agency (CISA) Binding Operational Directive (BOD) 22-01 findings, and the associated Common Vulnerabilities and Exposures (CVEs).</p>
